pageContext.claim: “Why aren't the same standards placed on the Democrats. Look what Hillary Clinton may have gotten away with. Disgraceful!”
pageContext.analysis: While there are some similarities between the Hillary Clinton's campaign's interactions with Ukrainians and Trump campaign's interactions with Russians, there are key differences that make it hard to compare the two. If Trump is referring to Clinton's handling of classified information as secretary of state, the FBI found that while she was "extremely careless," the agency found no evidence of intentional misconduct.
